**Professional Profile**
Ngoc Minh Nguyen is an aspiring professional in the information technology sector, currently pursuing a Major in Computer Science. As an AI Intern at the NLP & KD Lab, Ton Duc Thang University, Ngoc Minh was involved in a 2-member team to design and implement an AI-powered website. This role included integrating natural language interfaces, developing User and Admin Agents using LangChain, and focusing on end-to-end AI system design, FastAPI backend integration, and creating intuitive user experiences.

**Core Skills & Technology**
Proficient in a range of programming languages and AI frameworks, including Python, Langchain, Pytorch, Langgraph, Hugging Face, FastAPI, Scikit-learn, Pandas, and MongoDB.

**Education & Certifications**
Currently pursuing a Major in Computer Science at Ton Duc Thang University. Ngoc Minh has further enhanced expertise through certifications in Deep Research with LangGraph by LangChain Academy and Long-Term Agentic Memory with LangGraph by DeepLearning.AI.